m</strong></a>. Payment receipt can be downloaded directly from your account once your payment is confirmed by the committee.</p>\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --></p>', 'PVJ-ISHESSH 2020 – Bandung, Indonesia', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-01-03 08:46:12', '2020-01-03 08:46:12', '', 1, 'http://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/2020/01/03/1-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
