">Education</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Government Studies</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">International Relations</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Law</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Political Studies </span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Art &amp; Linguistics</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Religious Studies</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Sociology</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\"> and other related topics</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Keynote Speakers</strong></h3>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-102 size-thumbnail\" src=\"http://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Sayuti-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Muhammad Sayuti, Ph.D.</strong></p>\r\n<p>(Majelisdiktilitbang PP Muhammadiyah)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-129 size-thumbnail\" src=\"http://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Sakinah_Harith-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Prof. Sakinah Harith</strong></p>\r\n<p>(Universiti Sultan Zainal Abidin/UnisZa, Malaysia)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-130 size-thumbnail\" src=\"http://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Q0ZGODRFNEUtNjkwQS00RkQzLThBNDItMzMxMTVCMEIzNTUy-150x150.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Prof. Dr. Suswandari</strong></p>\r\n<p>(Universitas Muhammadiyah Prof.Dr.Hamka)</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-131 size-thumbnail\" src=\"http://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/YOS_2747-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Prof. Dr.Harun Joko Prayito 