bout innovation in health, economics, sosial science and humanities. In a more practical context, the conference is expected to become a platform of discussion among researchers, particularly the young ones, in the field of health, economics, sosial science and humanities. Therefore, the invited speakers in this conference are young researchers who have good reputation in the world.</p>\r\n<h2>SCOPE:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Public Health</li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Health Administration</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Hospitality</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Psychology</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Communication</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Economics</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Education</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Government Studies</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">International Relations</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Law</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Political Studies </span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Art &amp; Linguistics</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Religious Studies</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Sociology</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\"> and other related topics</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Keynote Speakers</strong></h3>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-102 \" src=\"http://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Sayuti-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"149\" height=\"149\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Muhammad Sayuti, Ph.D.</strong></p>\r\n<p>(Majelisdiktilitbang PP Muhammadiyah)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-143 size-thumbnail\" src=\"http://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/IMG-20200110-WA0006-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Assoc. Prof. Dr. Rosminah Binti Mohamed</strong></p>\r\n<p>(Universiti Sains Malaysia)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-130 size-thumbnail\" src=\"http://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Q0ZGODRFNEUtNjkwQS00RkQzLThBNDItMzMxMTVCMEIzNTUy-150x150.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Prof. Dr. Suswandari</strong></p>\r\n<p>(Universitas Muhammadiyah Prof.Dr.Hamka)</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-131 \" src=\"http://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/YOS_2747-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"152\" height=\"152\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Prof. Dr.Harun Joko Prayito , M.Hum.</strong></p>\r\n<p>(Universitas Muhammadiyah Surakarta)</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-106 size-thumbnail\" src=\"http://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Anna-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Prof. Dr. Anna Permanasari, M.Si. </strong></p>\r\n<p>(Universitas Pendidikan Indonesia)</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-107 size-thumbnail\" src=\"http://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Mamun-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Prof. Dr. Md. Mamun Habib</strong></p>\r\n<p>(Independent University Bangladesh)</p>\r\n<h3>Venue and Activities</h3>\r\n<p><strong>ASTON Pasteur Hotel, Baandung</strong></p>\r\n<p>Jl. Dr. Djunjunan No.162, Sukagalih, Kec. Sukajadi, Kota Bandung, Jawa Barat 40162</p>\r\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\r\n<h3>Important Date</h3>\r\n<p>Abstract Submission Deadline :February 14, 2020</p>\r\n<p>Notification ff Abstract Acceptance: February 21, 2020</p>\r\n<p>Payment Deadline: March 5, 2020</p>\r\n<p>Full Paper Submission Deadline: April 14, 2020</p>\r\n<p>Conference Day: April 15, 2020</p>\r\n<p>Full Paper Revision Submission Deadline: April 20, 2020</p>\r\n<h3>Registration Fee and Payment</h3>\r\n<p>The registration fees for conference below are for attending the conference only (not include hotel accommodation)</p>\r\n<p>[table id=2 /]</p>\r\n<p><strong>Please do bank transfer for the registration fee to</strong>:</p>\r\n<p>Bank Name: <strong>Bank BNI Syariah</strong></p>\r\n<p>Swift/ BIC: <strong>BNINDJA</strong></p>\r\n<p>Account Number: <strong>0613340113</strong></p>\r\n<p>Account Holder: <strong>Anggia Suci Pratiwi</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>[IMPORTANT] </strong>After making the payment, author <strong>MUST</strong><strong> </strong>upload the transfer proof via this website<strong> </strong><strong>(NOT Email)</strong>. Author can upload by logging in to our <a href=\"https://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/paper-submission/\"><strong>submission system</strong></a>. Payment receipt can be downloaded directly from your account once your payment is confirmed by the committee.</p>\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --></p>', 'PVJ-ISHESSH 2020 – Bandung, Indonesia', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-01-10 07:42:19', '2020-01-10 07:42:19', '', 1, 'http://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/2020/01/10/1-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
