ngs Indexed by Scopus/WoS. </strong>However, selected papers have the opportunity for publishing in Scopus Indexed Journals <strong>with additional charge</strong>.\r\n\r\nTherefore the author should follow the<strong> </strong><strong>article template.</strong> The papers should be written in English and must be between 4 to 6 pages.\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>DOWNLOAD PAPER TAMPLATE</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>BACKGROUND</h3>\r\nWelcome to the 1st Paris Van Java International Seminar on Health, Economics, Social Science and Humanities. Hosted by Universitas Muhammadiyah Tasikmalaya (UMTAS). The 1st PVJ-ISHESSH brings up <strong>“Innovation for better life”</strong> as its theme. The main purposes of the conference are (1) to bring together the scientists, researchers and practitioners, students, and civil society organization representatives in the scientific forum; and (2) to share and to discuss theoretical and practical knowledge about innovation in health, economics, sosial science and humanities. In a more practical context, the conference is expected to become a platform of discussion among researchers, particularly the young ones, in the field of health, economics, sosial science and humanities. Therefore, the invited speakers in this conference are young researchers who have good reputation in the world.\r\n<h2>SCOPE:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Public Health</li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Health Administration</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Hospitality</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Psychology</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Communication</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Economics</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Education</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Government Studies</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">International Relations</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Law</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Political Studies </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Art &amp; Linguistics</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Religious Studies</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">Sociology</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\"> and other related topics</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Keynote Speakers</strong></h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-102 \" src=\"http://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Sayuti-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"149\" height=\"149\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Muhammad Sayuti, Ph.D.</strong>\r\n\r\n(Majelisdiktilitbang PP Muhammadiyah)\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-143 size-thumbnail\" src=\"http://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/IMG-20200110-WA0006-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Assoc. Prof. Dr. Rosminah Binti Mohamed</strong>\r\n\r\n(Universiti Sains Malaysia)\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-130 size-thumbnail\" src=\"http://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Q0ZGODRFNEUtNjkwQS00RkQzLThBNDItMzMxMTVCMEIzNTUy-150x150.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Prof. Dr. Suswandari</strong>\r\n\r\n(Universitas Muhammadiyah Prof.Dr.Hamka)\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-131 \" src=\"http://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/YOS_2747-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"152\" height=\"152\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Prof. Dr.Harun Joko Prayito , M.Hum.</strong>\r\n\r\n(Universitas Muhammadiyah Surakarta)\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-106 size-thumbnail\" src=\"http://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Anna-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Prof. Dr. Anna Permanasari, M.Si. </strong>\r\n\r\n(Universitas Pendidikan Indonesia)\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-107 size-thumbnail\" src=\"http://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Mamun-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Prof. Dr. Md. Mamun Habib</strong>\r\n\r\n(Independent University Bangladesh)\r\n<h3>Venue and Activities</h3>\r\n<strong>ASTON Pasteur Hotel, Baandung</strong>\r\n\r\nJl. Dr. Djunjunan No.162, Sukagalih, Kec. Sukajadi, Kota Bandung, Jawa Barat 40162\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n<h3>Important Date</h3>\r\nAbstract Submission Deadline :February 14, 2020\r\n\r\nNotification ff Abstract Acceptance: February 21, 2020\r\n\r\nPayment Deadline: March 5, 2020\r\n\r\nFull Paper Submission Deadline: April 14, 2020\r\n\r\nConference Day: April 15, 2020\r\n\r\nFull Paper Revision Submission Deadline: April 20, 2020\r\n<h3>Registration Fee and Payment</h3>\r\nThe registration fees for conference below are for attending the conference only (not include hotel accommodation)\r\n\r\n[table id=2 /]\r\n\r\n<strong>Please do bank transfer for the registration fee to</strong>:\r\n\r\nBank Name: <strong>Bank BNI Syariah</strong>\r\n\r\nSwift/ BIC: <strong>BNINDJA</strong>\r\n\r\nAccount Number: <strong>0613340113</strong>\r\n\r\nAccount Holder: <strong>Anggia Suci Pratiwi</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>[IMPORTANT] </strong>After making the payment, author <strong>MUST</strong><strong> </strong>upload the transfer proof via this website<strong> </strong><strong>(NOT Email)</strong>. Author can upload by logging in to our <a href=\"https://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/paper-submission/\"><strong>submission system</strong></a>. Payment receipt can be downloaded directly from your account once your payment is confirmed by the committee.\r\n\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'PVJ-ISHESSH 2020 – Bandung, Indonesia', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-01-14 03:20:43', '2020-01-14 03:20:43', '', 1, 'http://pvj-is.umtas.ac.id/hessh/2020/01/14/1-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
